.Fn auth_destroy "AUTH *auth"
.Xc
.Pp
A macro that destroys the authentication information associated with
.Fa auth .
Destruction usually involves deallocation of private data
structures.
The use of
.Fa auth
is undefined after calling
.Fn auth_destroy .
.Pp
